sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor AT as Attendee
    participant EP as Event Page
    participant DJ as Django Web App
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant ES as Email Server

    AT ->> EP: Complete Payment for an Order
    EP ->> DJ: Request Event Confirmation
    DJ ->> PG: Query Order Number
    PG -->> DJ: Return Order Number
    DJ ->> ES: Request Email Confirmation
    ES -->> DJ: Send Confirmation
    DJ -->> EP: Send Order Number and Confirmation
    EP -->> AT: Display Order Number and Confirmation,<br>along with a link to help/support or resend
